law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 3, effective March 21, 1960. -- Created 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 7, Art. XII, sec. 2, effective March 29, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Duty of commission to study Constitution; recommendations; reports; assist constitutional convention.
